Enchantment
Levels: Cleric 2, Paladin 2
Components: V, S
Range: Medium
Target: Allies in a 20-ft.-radius burst
Duration: 1 minute/level

Allies gain a +1 bonus to their Dodge AC and saving throws. This spell does not affect the caster.

<i>You call upon your holy powers to aid your companions and a golden light appears from above, bathing them with sparkling radiance.</i>